Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,(You'll shine like a diamond)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把时间稍微推前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,（图陆镇）
把时间稍微推前
